Kafka - distributed event store and realtime streaming platform .
producer sends the message to the kafka brokers then costumer group use when needed. 
message - 1. headers - carry meta data
2. key- helps org 
3. value - deploy payload 
in broker the message are diveded into topics 
advantages - handles multiple data , different consumer groups to read from same topic, can resume from failure in a process if you are left in middle .
Kafka produer - batch messages to cut down a network traffic . 
